Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:17.55,Spike,,0,0,0,,Spike is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:19.81,Spike,,0,0,0,,Making a jewel cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:24.57,Spike,,0,0,0,,Me, that's who.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:26.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,Been saving up my gems so fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:28.90,Spike,,0,0,0,,For a cake that is divine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:32.66,Spike,,0,0,0,,Who are you whoing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:36.44,Spike,,0,0,0,,I know they're delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.37,0:00:41.92,Spike,,0,0,0,,Now you see them, now… you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:47.74,Spike,,0,0,0,,This is how you make a jewel cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:50.33,Spike,,0,0,0,,Stir in some gems and then you bake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:55.05,Spike,,0,0,0,,Gonna eat-eat-eat it up. Gonna…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:58.73,Spike,,0,0,0,,What happened to all my jewels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:04.74,Spike,,0,0,0,,I had a bowl full of them here, and now I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:07.61,Spike,,0,0,0,,Which means somebody took 'em…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.01,0:01:12.39,Spike,,0,0,0,,Who?! That's what I'm asking, who!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.39,0:01:14.66,Spike,,0,0,0,,Who took my jewels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:18.79,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh. I'm who.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:21.31,Spike,,0,0,0,,This cake was gonna be so good…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:22.21,Spike,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:24.42,Spike,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.16,0:01:33.70,Spike,,0,0,0,,WHYYYYY?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:15.84,Spike,,0,0,0,,I have no jewels,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:17.87,Spike,,0,0,0,,I have no cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:22.54,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm a sad little dragon with nothing to…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:24.65,Spike,,0,0,0,,…is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:30.09,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh goodness. I… I hope I'm not interrupting anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:33.53,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, I do have this cake to not bake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:36.05,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, it's a bad time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:38.18,Spike,,0,0,0,,Inside joke. Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:40.70,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It's just that… Princess Cadance needs us to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:44.86,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,do a great job welcoming the head of the Equestria Games when she visits the Crystal Empire tomorrow…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:48.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know all about that.\N As if I wouldn't be any help at welcoming…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:50.74,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know what was I thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.74,0:02:53.42,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Of course you might be upset for not being invited, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:56.28,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,here I am coming ask you for a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:58.84,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You were probably going to say no anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:01.73,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,All I had to offer you in exchange was just one little jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:03.00,Spike,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:08.00,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,All I have is this jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:13.40,Spike,,0,0,0,,That's a really big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:18.86,Spike,,0,0,0,,A really big, juicy, perfect-for-a-cake-topper jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:20.65,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Does this mean you'll do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:22.47,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:26.60,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you, thank you!\NSo while I'm gone, you'll take care of Angel,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:31.72,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,and tomorrow is Tuesday which is his tail-fluffing day,\Nand it's really important for him to look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:35.22,Spike,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? You want me to take care of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:38.72,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:45.18,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But, if it's too much trouble, I can always see if there is somepony else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:49.94,Spike,,0,0,0,,We already agreed on the whole jewel thing, so I'll just…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:52.31,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:54.96,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Angel, aren't you just so excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:00.69,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:08.94,Spike,,0,0,0,,You know… She's not the only pony with a pet that might need some watching…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:16.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,All I'm saying is, if Fluttershy thought that her beloved little friend shouldn't be left alone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:20.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,while you're busy in the Crystal Empire, then, maybe that's just something to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:25.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Tank's not some fuzzy little bunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:32.16,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,He can take care of himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:36.08,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,He is a strong, fearless and totally together pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:59.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Alright, you can watch him, but only because…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:05.01,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Tank's got a strict flying regiment and, and someone needs to make sure that he doesn't slack off while I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:14.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You know, the two of us are very diligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:16.50,Spike,,0,0,0,,Ok, ok, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:20.90,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes and more importantly, as for Opal, she likes to eat every 36.5 minutes…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:23.04,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You groom her with her silken brush head to tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:25.87,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And don't forget to put her pillow in the middle, that's where she likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:29.99,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, and the temperature in the room should always be exactly 81.4 degrees,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:32.28,Rarity,,0,0,0,,that's the only way she can get to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:35.09,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And… oh, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:38.03,Rarity,,0,0,0,,So, thanks for the help and good luck to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:45.11,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I think the dragon was expecting a little something for his efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:53.40,Spike,,0,0,0,,Almost as beautiful as the pony who gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:56.06,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be critter-proofing the library or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:58.21,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Tank has a tendency to…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:03.11,Spike,,0,0,0,,Critter-proofing…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:05.34,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll get right on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:08.31,Spike,,0,0,0,,Three down, three to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.37,Spike,,0,0,0,,What's that you said, Gummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:15.39,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, you're just gonna have to ask Pinkie Pie about that one
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:16.77,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Ask me, ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.87,Spike,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:24.02,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Of course you can have another cupcake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:32.01,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Why didn't you say so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:35.84,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'll get you a bigger pond immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:38.30,Spike,,0,0,0,,I think what Gummy's trying to say is…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:40.20,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,He always wanted a pair of riding pants?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:42.09,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,His toenails need a new coat of shellac?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:44.84,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,He wants to floss twice a day instead of just once?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.25,Spike,,0,0,0,,I think what Gummy's trying to say
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:49.59,Spike,,0,0,0,,is that he'd like a little Spike time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:52.83,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Who wouldn't? Spike time is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:55.86,Spike,,0,0,0,,Alas, it doesn't come cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:07:00.36,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,All I'm saying is that you might wanna think about a helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.36,0:07:04.74,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You only wanna get hit in a head by a flying turtle… once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:09.51,Spike,,0,0,0,,A thousand plus carats of pure deliciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:16.01,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Looks like you got a regular pet day care in here, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:19.84,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You'll still be able to get some good play time with Winona, like you said though, won't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:22.76,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,She tends to get a little wild if she doesn't get her exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:24.73,Spike,,0,0,0,,Exercise. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:28.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't remember seeing critters on the invite list.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:30.52,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause we're leaving them here with Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:32.88,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,He's gonna do a little critter-sitting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:34.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:43.09,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,So sorry I'm late.\NSilly bunny had hidden his brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:47.05,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Be sure you get plenty on his tail, or it won't get as poofy as he likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:50.02,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Come on, girls, or we're gonna miss the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:52.14,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,One more for the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:54.14,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Come on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:56.09,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I love you more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:57.82,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,No, I love you more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:07:59.38,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I LOVE YOU MORE!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.57,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, I promise it'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:08.14,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'll fluff your tail twice next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.47,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Three times?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:15.87,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I know. It's a chilly 81.2 in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:18.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Spike, take care of this, would you please?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:19.24,Spike,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:23.44,Spike,,0,0,0,,So, uhh… What are you thinking about that hooting little friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.71,Spike,,0,0,0,,Suppose you want me to keep an eye on him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:29.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That would be nice. You sure you don't already have your hands full?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:32.13,Spike,,0,0,0,,Nah, p'shaw. I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:34.70,Spike,,0,0,0,,But, uh, just between you and me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:38.31,Spike,,0,0,0,,I gotta give priority to the… paying customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:44.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You absolutely sure you can do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:48.10,Spike,,0,0,0,,Of course. Wouldn't have agreed to it if I couldn't. Piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:51.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,Speaking of cake, I got a little something I need to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:55.39,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like keeping an eye on a house full of critters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:59.35,Spike,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah, that was totally what I was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:02.65,Spike,,0,0,0,,Relax. Go to your welcoming thing in the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:04.83,Spike,,0,0,0,,Spike's got it all under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:41.15,Spike,,0,0,0,,Alright sidekicks, front and center!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.71,Spike,,0,0,0,,There are six of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:47.25,Spike,,0,0,0,,but there's only one right here in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.19,Spike,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:50.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,And what I say, goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:53.94,Spike,,0,0,0,,Spike, the boss of you, that's who.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:55.76,Spike,,0,0,0,,One, two, three…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:09:59.54,Spike,,0,0,0,,C'mon, number four!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:07.61,Spike,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:09.82,Spike,,0,0,0,,Who's missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:13.90,Spike,,0,0,0,,Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:19.96,Spike,,0,0,0,,All I wanted were some jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:21.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,Big, juicy, delicious jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:24.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,Now what do I have? A missing rabbit, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:31.44,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Little fluffy Angel bunnykins,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.18,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,you're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:36.26,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,These natural waves and its fluff are to die for!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:44.60,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Isn't Angel just the cutest thing you've ever seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:51.44,Spike,,0,0,0,,Look. You don't wanna be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:55.36,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not chase you around all over the place when I could be enjoing some jewel cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:58.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,Watch me solve both of our problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:11:01.84,Spike,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm supposed to be watching him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:05.19,Spike,,0,0,0,,but you all just had it all so well that maybe,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:08.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,maybe I could let you take care of him instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:13.42,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,We would, but we've got some major Crusaders business planned for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:17.67,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Major. Me're getting our skydiving cutie marks today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:22.45,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose if you've got other plans…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.93,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's just you're so good with him, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:27.86,Spike,,0,0,0,,get-our-cutie-mark-for-bunny-sitting good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:29.98,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,A bunny-sitting cutie mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:33.13,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,That would be adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.12,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,It does seem to like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:40.18,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And we haven't exactly figured out how we're gonna pull off this whole skydiving thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:44.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,You know what? As hard as it's gonna be for me to part with these little guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.36,Spike,,0,0,0,,I think you should probably just take all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.36,0:11:50.55,Spike,,0,0,0,,If you ask me, the more critters you take care of,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:54.76,Spike,,0,0,0,,the more chances you have of getting some kind of critter-sitting cutie mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:57.05,Spike,,0,0,0,,Am I right, or am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:00.24,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:01.47,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:05.52,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But wait! How are we gonna take good care of 'em without treats for them when they're good?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:07.60,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,And we'll need beds for when they're tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.38,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,And toys! They need toys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:13.25,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's an afternoon! Thay don't need all that stuff. They'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:15.68,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,We need to be able to buy them some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:18.38,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,One jewel might be able to cover it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:21.94,Spike,,0,0,0,,What would I possibly be doing with jewels?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:24.04,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I happen to know for a fact
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:26.76,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,that Applejack gave you a gem to watch Winona.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:28.90,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Which means…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:32.80,Spike,,0,0,0,,Obviously, no one around here is getting her cutiemark for kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:35.13,Spike,,0,0,0,,towards a poor hungry little dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:36.37,Spike,,0,0,0,,Take it or leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:37.77,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,We'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:46.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,Gonna put in some flour and add a little sugar for my five delicious jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:51.28,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,But pink feathers would look so good with your eyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,That bird could use a little color…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:56.41,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Has anyone seen Tank's head?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:12:57.82,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Where's his head?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:00.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,What have you done to the turtle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:04.88,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Oh, I totally forgot he could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:10.86,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so pretty sure critter-sitting cutiemarks are out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:16.18,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,And our critter-grooming cutiemarks probably aren't going to appear anytime soon either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:19.83,Spike,,0,0,0,,All right, load em up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:22.06,Spike,,0,0,0,,And you can give me back that jewel I gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:24.57,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Sorry, we don't have it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:25.96,Spike,,0,0,0,,What? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:29.56,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,How do you think we paid for the industrial-sized pet hair dryer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:52.19,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Zecora knows just what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:55.52,Zecora,,0,0,0,,about all this bad mojo that's floating around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:59.47,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking a cage and a great big lock might be next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:01.52,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Zecora can take the bad away
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:03.32,Zecora,,0,0,0,,if you do just what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.03,Spike,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:06.24,Zecora,,0,0,0,,But before I can do my duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:08.43,Zecora,,0,0,0,,I'm going to need some of your booty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:15.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:17.91,Zecora,,0,0,0,,You think jewels are what you need,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:21.04,Zecora,,0,0,0,,but there's no worse mojo than dragon's greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:43.74,Spike,,0,0,0,,Almost there…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:51.53,Spike,,0,0,0,,Just taking good care of everyone's animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:57.59,Spike,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna have to do to get this to go away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:05.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,Then it's just between you and me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:07.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,No other pony has to hear a word about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:12.59,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Hear a word about what, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:18.99,Spike,,0,0,0,,This better be important.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:22.87,Somepony,,0,0,0,,All aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.22,Spike,,0,0,0,,Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:30.39,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I can't have all these animals on my train.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:32.80,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Not without tickets, and not without chaperones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:36.92,Spike,,0,0,0,,All I need is to get on for one minute, grab a bunny and get off! Promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:38.61,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Likely story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.61,0:15:41.80,Somepony,,0,0,0,,No chaperone, no train.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:47.12,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Skydiving cutie marks, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:50.92,Spike,,0,0,0,,Is three ponies enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:58.81,Spike,,0,0,0,,At least I have you two left, my delectable little treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:02.99,Somepony,,0,0,0,,All aboard for the Crystal Empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:05.03,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Crystal Empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:07.96,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to see the Crystal Empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:11.67,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I wish I had dressed for it, but still…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:13.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,We're not really going!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:15.65,Spike,,0,0,0,,We just needed to get on the train so I can get that rabbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,and when I do, we're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:18.59,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,What's?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:20.85,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,It's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:22.76,Spike,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:27.84,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Next stop is the Crystal Empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:30.24,Spike,,0,0,0,,No no no no no no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:39.03,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,So it seems like the Crystal Empire would be really cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:42.56,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,but I've heard it's not! It's as warm as it can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:44.57,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Do you think the walls are crystal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:48.11,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Maybe even see-through! Imagine see-through walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:02.57,Spike,,0,0,0,,Take it! Just take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:11.06,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,So… beautiful…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:14.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, enjoy while you can, cause we're not getting out of this car until we're back in Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.47,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,There's no way, no how,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:21.56,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,we're coming all the way to the Crystal Empire without looking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:24.39,Spike,,0,0,0,,Nopony is gonna get past this dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:28.17,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Don't make me use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:30.18,Spike,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:43.98,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:58.00,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Wow! Just… wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:18:00.40,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I'm in crystal heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:02.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,They're right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:07.45,Spike,,0,0,0,,There's the bunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:11.00,Spike,,0,0,0,,Please, please, pretty please, don't go down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:16.96,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'll fluff your tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:21.80,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'll perm it and blow it out for you! Just stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:25.05,Spike,,0,0,0,,What do you want? Name it, and it's yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:40.34,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh my goodness…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:41.90,Somepony,,0,0,0,,All aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:46.96,Spike,,0,0,0,,You're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:50.34,Spike,,0,0,0,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:52.53,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Without seeing the palace…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:54.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think this car's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:57.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,They're coming this way. Everybody, down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:02.01,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,There has to be a better solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.15,Spike,,0,0,0,,Don't sit down, don't sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:08.58,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,My dogs are barking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:12.98,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Did y'all hear that? They really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:18.53,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Bummer Spike had to miss out on all this. He would have fun here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:22.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's having a great time watching all the critters back at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:24.65,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Think he has still got a handle on things?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If he's staying calm and collected,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:30.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I bet he's doing a terrific job as a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:36.75,Spike,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, bunny. Do your worst. I deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:42.90,Spike,,0,0,0,,I ignored you, tried to pawn you off on someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:46.81,Spike,,0,0,0,,I didn't take these silly things out, or fluff this like I was supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:50.79,Spike,,0,0,0,,I wasn't really thinking about you at all. Any of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:52.66,Spike,,0,0,0,,Just wanted the jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:55.98,Spike,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll all forgive me some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:58.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:02.92,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:05.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the one who gives us away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:14.51,Spike,,0,0,0,,Where did you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:16.36,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Y'all hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.34,0:20:32.00,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to scratch the belly of Winona! Oh, I miss her…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:34.74,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see Owlowiscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:36.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:39.94,Spike,,0,0,0,,Thought we'd meet you at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:42.09,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,So we could hear all about the Crystal Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:44.36,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,and find out if you brought us one of the crystal snowglobes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:45.98,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,that they sell at the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:48.42,Rarity,,0,0,0,,How did you know about the snowglobes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:53.03,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Lucky guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've got to hand it to you, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:58.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You did a really good job of taking care of the animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:03.28,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spike, Angel looks perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:05.94,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You did such a good job fluffing his tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:08.53,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, more like this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:11.02,Spike,,0,0,0,,You know who.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:18.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So, what're you thinking? Baking a new jewel pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:21.78,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Ooh, six-layer gem cake sounds pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:23.36,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:25.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,Really, really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:30.55,Spike,,0,0,0,,WHYYYYYYYYYYYY?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:34.83,Somepony,,0,0,0,,SCHASTLIVYI PONETC
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:38.93,Somepony,,0,0,0,,anon2anon \N sunnysubs.com
